data.description: You will have COUNTRY LIVING CLOSE TO TOWN with this "like new" home situated on just over an acre. House has 2304 sq. ft. and includes 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Nice open floor plan features a beautiful kitchen complete with all appliances, a large island with electricity and a pantry. Living area is a great size and has a pretty stone wood burning fireplace. Large mud room/laundry room. Isolated master ensuite has double sinks, a soaker tub and separate shower.  Every room in this well cared for home is large and has great storage. Outside features include a storage shed, large backyard with privacy fence, deck and above ground pool. Call today to for an appointment.
